
<div class="container flex-grow-1" id="homepage">
  <div class="details-section">
    <h1 class="name">Emily Hoult</h1>
    <div class="title-box col-7 p-0">
      <p class="title">UI/UX Designer & Frontend Developer</p>
    </div>
    <button class="btn btn-primary" id="cv-btn">Download CV</button>
  </div>

  <div class="d-flex svgs circle">
    <%= image_tag("circle.svg", class: "circle-svg") %>
    <%= image_tag("p-dot-1.svg", class: "p-dot-1") %>
  </div>

  <div class="about-section d-flex flex-wrap">
    <div class="row p-0">
      <h1 class="col-12 about" id="about">About</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="row p-0">
      <div class="col-7 p-0">
        <p class="pr-4">
          Hi, I’m Emily, a UI/UX Designer with a background in Fashion Merchandising and E-commerce. I’m British/German, grew up in the Netherlands and have been living and working in Berlin for the past 4 years.
          <br>
          <br>
          I love that UI design brings out my creativity and attention to detail and I’m passionate about designing seamless, intuitive and elegant solutions. I’m a problem solver with an eye for detail and I love
          the idea of being able to calm interfaces and improve the user experience through the use of structure, patterns and whitespace.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="col-5 p-0">
       <%= image_tag("emilyhoult.jpg", class: "emilyhoult") %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

    <div class="d-flex svgs triangle">
